product.name: Edelrid Tommy Caldwell Pro DuoTec 9.6mm Dry Rope
product.description: This Edelrid Pro DuoTec 9.6mm dry rope was developed together with top climber Tommy Caldwell. Its very high sheath proportion makes it ideal for working routes or big-wall climbing.

product.name: La Sportiva Katana Lace Climbing Shoes

product.name: Wild Country Friend Cam Set - #0.4, 0.5, 0.75, 1, 2, 3

product.name: Eddyline Caribbean 12 FS Sit-On-Top Kayak

product.description: Having fun on the water is easy with the 11 ft. SIC Maui TAO Air Glide inflatable stand up paddle board, a versatile touring design that's as great for the whole family as it is for solo exploring.

product.name: Roxy 2/2 mm Syncro Back-Zip Springsuit - Women's
product.description: Perfect for shoulder-season swims and surf sessions, the women's Roxy 2/2 mm Syncro Back-Zip springsuit takes the edge off those cold morning temps so you can stay in the water longer.

product.name: Kelty Discovery 4 Tent
product.description: When you pack up the Subie for a few days of car camping or music fest-ing, you're not worried about traveling light—you wanna travel right. That means you want the 3-season Kelty Discovery 4 tent.

product.name: ENO DoubleNest Printed Hammock
product.description: With ample room for 2, the ever-popular ENO DoubleNest Printed hammock assembles in seconds and is light enough to take backpacking, while being robust enough for backyard hangout sessions.
